522
00:33:55,480 --> 00:33:57,480
- Precisely.
- That's right.

523
00:33:57,480 --> 00:34:00,119
You weren't there back then.

524
00:34:00,120 --> 00:34:01,399
If you were there,

525
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:04,060
