526
00:34:04,060 --> 00:34:05,540
That's impossible!

527
00:34:07,080 --> 00:34:10,839
Me? It's impossible for me to break their bones.

528
00:34:10,839 --> 00:34:14,879
I would surely snap all of their necks,

529
00:34:14,879 --> 00:34:17,120
