567
00:36:55,320 --> 00:36:58,139
My 10 years' worth of effort has gone down the drain!

568
00:36:58,160 --> 00:36:59,519
This won't do!

569
00:36:59,520 --> 00:37:01,399
I need to avenge him.

570
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:03,039
