592
00:38:13,139 --> 00:38:15,319
Can't I retaliate when she was the one who struck me first?

593
00:38:15,320 --> 00:38:17,979
That's right. Of course not.

594
00:38:18,680 --> 00:38:22,359
Because... Because you follow the villains' code of ethics, right?

595
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:26,320
You said so yourself. You'll never kill anyone who cannot defend themselves.

596
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:28,119
Am I right?

597
00:38:28,120 --> 00:38:29,879
That's right!

598
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:32,560
